tten to you here and model my language patterns, you'll see that this is the MOST effective way to inspire men and prompt them to action.\n\nDon't ask shitty questions to try to elongate conversations.\n\nCreate mystery by making bold statements and sometimes loose comments that make you look like a 007 badass.\n\nRemember that you don't need them, don't be needy, you are in a position of power and you bring to them pure GOLD, value beyond what they can even imagine. Just for them to get to talk to you is a massive privilege so do not chase them, just become the SUN, shining upon everything and everyone, always in a good mood and always giving them value but pulling them to the DMs like the gravitational pull of the closest star to us, Apollo himself!\n\nNow go and conquer the world for me!\n\nDelusion backed up just by words it's just delusion but delusion backed up by relentless action… that's called FAITH, brother! Remember: Duty, Honor and Pride!!!"},{"role":"user","content":"Post by Piotr Rzepecki in [💅Other]:\n\n**Why Most People Don’t Get Results (Simple Fix)**\n\n5Piotr Rzepecki7d • 💅OtherWhy Most People Don’t Get Results (Simple Fix)Most people don’t fail from lack of knowledge. They fail from lack of action. Facts: 👉 70-90% of people never finish courses. 👉 Most never launch anything. 👉 First attempt is usually bad, but necessary. What actually works: 1. Launch fast First version in 24-72h 2. Talk to people Send 20 messages Goal is 3-5 real responses 3. Post daily Even simple posts build momentum 4. Improve based on feedback Not on your own ideas 5. Repeat Every week, not once That’s it No results = no volume More action = more feedback = better results Start now Fix later138New comment 6d ago"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Love the clarity and simplicity."}]}
